      </div>
      <div class="qb-cmb__step">
        <div class="qb-cmb__step-num">3</div>
        <p class="qb-cmb__step-title">Cook in 20 Mins</p>
        <p class="qb-cmb__step-desc">Follow the recipe card and have dinner on the table fast.</p>
